title: Ranked 5 Looking for JG
body:
The XxxNew World OrderxxX is running a little short of members right now and we are looking for a jungler to complete us.
We are looking for a jungler main of any rank, the only real requirements is that we are planning to be a serious yet still looking to have fun team and you need to be online  for a fair amount of time.

If you are interested send me an invite my IGN is: Pandadude123
